---
title: Chicken & Mushroom Truffle Gnocchi with Garlicky Panko & Parmesan
description: Treat yourself to truffles with tonight’s ‘shroom-packed pasta. You’ll start with pillowy potato gnocchi, which you’ll cook until tender, then toss in a silky, savory sauce of sautéed button mushrooms, garlic powder, mushroom stock, cream cheese, and Parmesan. A swirl of butter and dusting of truffle zest take the rich and umami flavors to the next level. Garnish everything with crunchy, garlicky panko, then pour yourself a glass of wine and toast to a restaurant-worthy dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/62a9ee9bd7b76fed540a48c7-eff972dd.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/chicken-mushroom-truffle-gnocchi-62a9ee9bd7b76fed540a48c7-03a79a5b.pdf
servings: 2
cuisine: Italian
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/chicken-and-mushroom-truffle-gnocchi-62a9ee9bd7b76fed540a48c7
course: main course
time required: 20 minutes
author: HelloFresh
